897.1, 1112.4, 917.9]}, {"text": "result of overall market risk aversion, lack of demand for securities that are non-government guaranteed, and the", "bbox": [162.5, 922.1, 1112.4, 942.9]}, {"text": "relative widening of credit spreads relative to the U.S. treasuries. The Company believes that it will be able to", "bbox": [162.5, 947.1, 1112.5, 967.9]}, {"text": "collect all principal and interest amounts due at maturity given the high credit quality of these investments. Since", "bbox": [162.5, 972.1, 1112.4, 992.9]}, {"text": "the decline in the market value is attributable to changes in market conditions and not credit quality, and since the", "bbox": [162.5, 997.1, 1112.4, 1017.9]}, {"text": "Company has the ability and intent to hold those investments until a recovery of par value, which may be", "bbox": [162.5, 1022.1, 1112.5, 1042.9]}, {"text": "maturity, the Company does not consider these investments to be other-than temporarily impaired as of", "bbox": [162.5, 1047.1, 1112.5, 1067.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2008.", "bbox": [162.5, 1072.1, 331.6, 1092.9]}, {"text": "In February 2008, auctions began to fail for these securities and each auction since then has failed.", "bbox": [204.2, 1115.3, 1112.3, 1136.2]}, {"text": "Approximately 10% of the Company’s investments portfolio comprises of these ARS, whose underlying assets", "bbox": [162.5, 1140.3, 1112.4, 1161.2]}, {"text": "are student loans which are substantially backed by the federal government. After the initial issuance of the", "bbox": [162.5, 1165.3, 1112.4, 1186.2]}, {"text": "securities, the interest rate on the securities is reset periodically, at intervals established at the time of issuance", "bbox": [162.5, 1190.3, 1112.4, 1211.2]}, {"text": "(primarily every twenty-eight days), based on market demand for a reset period. Auction-rate securities are", "bbox": [162.5, 1215.3, 1112.4, 1236.2]}, {"text": "bought and sold in the marketplace through a competitive bidding process often referred to as a “Dutch auction.”", "bbox": [162.5, 1240.3, 1112.4, 1261.2]}, {"text": "If there is insufficient interest in the securities at the time of an auction, the auction may not be completed and the", "bbox": [162.5, 1265.3, 1112.4, 1286.2]}, {"text": "rates may be reset to predetermined “penalty” or “maximum” rates based on mathematical formulas in", "bbox": [162.5, 1290.3, 1112.5, 1311.2]}, {"text": "accordance with each security’s prospectus.", "bbox": [162.5, 1315.3, 528.1, 1336.2]}, {"text": "Consequently, the investments are not currently liquid. All ARS are currently rated AAA, the highest rating,", "bbox": [204.2, 1358.6, 1112.4, 1379.4]}, {"text": "except for one which is rated A2, by a rating agency. The Company does not expect the need to access these", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.6, 1112.4, 1404.4]}, {"text": "funds in the short-term; however, in the event the Company needed to access these funds, they are not expected", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.6, 1112.4, 1429.4]}, {"text": "to be accessible until one of the following occurs: a successful auction occurs, the issuer redeems the issue, a", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.6, 1112.5, 1454.4]}, {"text": "68", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}